      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CABAO MARBLE (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (24.08) in a Other at Gawler. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Has ability and looks hard to stop. WIRRULLA HARRY (1) ran fourth in a Special conditions race last time, copping a check in the run and finishing 6 lengths from the winner over 342m at this track. Has two wins from Box 1. Speedy runner and should be in the action early from the inside. May be worth another try. I'M MY DESIGN (4) was a (20.19) winner last time out at this track from Box 1. Has good early speed so she should be prominent despite the squeeze draw. Expected to measure up again. CHRISTOFF (7) is another with top-three prospects.",
